languages.text: "Ему лучше, Лорд-капитан. Корабельный хирургеон был поражен его выносливостью. Почтенный господин Ульфар оправляется от ран в своих покоях".
"He is feeling better, Lord Captain. The ship's chirurgeon was amazed at his resilience. The esteemed Lord Ulfar is currently convalescing in his chambers."

languages.text: « Il va mieux, {mf|seigneur-capitaine|seigneure-capitaine}. Sa résistance a même énormément surpris le chirurgeon du bord. L'honorable seigneur Ulfar est actuellement en convalescence dans ses quartiers. »

traits.locale_text: « Il va mieux, {mf|seigneur-capitaine|seigneure-capitaine}. Sa résistance a même énormément surpris le médecin du bord. L'honorable maître Ulfar est actuellement dans ses quartiers, où il se remet de ses blessures. »

languages.text: “他正在逐渐康复，舰长大人。他的恢复能力让所有医生惊讶不已，尊敬的乌尔法大人目前正在他的房间里养伤。”
languages.original_text: "He is feeling better, Lord Captain. The ship's chirurgeon was amazed at his resilience. The esteemed Lord Ulfar is currently convalescing in his chambers."

traits.locale_text: “他正在逐渐康复，舰长大人。他的恢复能力让所有医生惊讶不已，尊敬的乌尔法大师目前正在他的房间里养伤。”

languages.text: "Es geht ihm besser, Lord Captain. Der Chirurgeum des Schiffs war erstaunt über seine Widerstandsfähigkeit. Der geschätzte Lord Ulfar erholt sich derzeit in seinen Gemächern."
languages.original_text: "He is feeling better, Lord Captain. The ship's chirurgeon was amazed at his resilience. The esteemed Lord Ulfar is currently convalescing in his chambers."

traits.locale_text: "Es geht ihm besser, Lord Captain. Der Chirurgeum des Schiffs war erstaunt über seine Widerstandsfähigkeit. Der ehrenhafte Meister Ulfar erholt sich augenblicklich in seinen Gemächern von den Verletzungen."

languages.text: «Se encuentra mejor, Lord Capitán. El cirujano de la nave se quedó sorprendido con su resistencia. En estos momentos, el honorable maestro Ulfar se está recuperando en sus aposentos».
languages.original_text: "He is feeling better, Lord Captain. The ship's chirurgeon was amazed at his resilience. The esteemed Lord Ulfar is currently convalescing in his chambers."

languages.text: 「彼は回復しております、ロード・キャプテン。船のチラージョンがあの回復力に驚いていました。ご立派なウルファー様は現在、部屋で休養中です」
languages.original_text: "He is feeling better, Lord Captain. The ship's chirurgeon was amazed at his resilience. The esteemed Lord Ulfar is currently convalescing in his chambers."

languages.text: "Daha iyi Lord Kaptan. Dirayetiyle geminin cerrahını şaşırtıyor. Saygıdeğer Lord Ulfar, şu an odasında toparlanmaya çalışıyor."
languages.original_text: "He is feeling better, Lord Captain. The ship's chirurgeon was amazed at his resilience. The esteemed Lord Ulfar is currently convalescing in his chambers."
